works.description:
This user is using this album to point  
ebay buyers to extra pictures of a camper he is fraudulently  
listing/selling on eBay.
He is a fraudulent seller as he does not own the camper to sell; I, Jamie 

Hobbis, am the legal owner and registered keeper of said vehicle.

He acquired these images from me last year posing as a prospective buyer  

via the website listed above.

Ebay have been informed and are conducting a fraud investigation.

All images of my camper are infringements of my copyright as I took all
the  
photos displayed in the album.
